Package chess

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Board
    Board is a representation of the current state of the game board.
    Chess
    Main class that creates a game instance and starts the chess game.
    Game
    Game represents an instance of a chess game Contains method that controls the game, keeps track of turns, valid moves, checks etc.
    Square
    Square represents an individual block inside of board.
